'''Bug Meat''' is a [[Monster Loot]] item which is dropped from any type of [[Adventurer's Guild#Cave Insect|insect]], including [[Armored Bug]]s and [[Armored Bug (dangerous)|dangerous Armored Bugs]] if the player has forged their weapon with a [[Forge#Combat enchantments|Bug Killer enchantment]].

[[Dorado]], [[Lingcod]], or [[Pike]] [[Fish Pond]]s may produce 20 Bug Meat when the population of the pond reaches 9.

