==Bundles==
Bug Meat is not used in any [[Bundles|bundles]].

==Tailoring==
Bug Meat is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{name|Shirt027|link=Tailoring{{!}}Pink Striped Shirt|class=inline}}. It is a dark pink dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the purple dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*10 Bug Meat may be requested by several fish in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].
*[[Willy]] requests 100 Bug Meat in the [[Quests#Juicy Bugs Wanted|"Juicy Bugs Wanted!"]] Special Order. The rewards are {{Price|3000}} and the [[Quality Bobber]] recipe.

==History==
{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}
{{History|1.4|Used as an ingredient to the [[Sturdy Ring]] recipe.  Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].  Can be requested in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]]. Can be produced by [[Fish Pond|Fish Ponds]].}}
{{History|1.5|Needed in the [[Quests#Juicy Bugs Wanted|"Juicy Bugs Wanted!" Special Order]]. Used as an ingredient to the [[Bug Steak]] and [[Magic Bait]] recipes.}}

